  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Reviewing App Structure**\n\nI\'m currently reviewing the file structure and laying the groundwork for \"Lernwelt,\" a German language learning app for Grades 1-4. My focus is on the app\'s overall structure and its key components. I\'m prioritizing user intent above all else, starting with a clear overview of the required and desired components. My focus is to be comprehensive and complete at this stage.\n\n\n**Listing Available Skills**\n\nI\'m now listing available skills for \"Lernwelt.\" I\'ve ruled out cloud SQL, as local storage seems sufficient. Firebase is also currently off the table, allowing us to maintain a client-side SPA with localStorage for user state management, with some AI assistance. The focus is now on making the app responsive, elegant, and interactive, while maintaining a user-friendly experience. I\'m exploring integration with Gemini for optional AI-driven exercises, but the core functionality will be local.\n\n\n**Analyzing Design Specifications**\n\nI\'ve discovered a comprehensive design spec for \"Lernwelt\", including colors, typography, and component details. I\'m now cross-referencing this with the image-generation skill to explore potential mascot and icon creation, using Lucide icons where applicable. A skill check confirms image generation as relevant.\n\n\n"
