  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Designing the Mascot**\n\nI\'m currently focused on the Mascot component, aiming for a friendly creature named Lumi built with Tailwind SVG elements. The goal is an interactive experience, potentially placed in the instruction card, with animations like blinking eyes, smiling mouth, and flapping. I am exploring different ways to accomplish this.\n\n\n**Refining the UI**\n\nI\'ve been working on UI components! I\'ve visualized the Mascot with dynamic SVG expressions that indicate correctness. The LessonMap is now an S-curve progress map with circular icons, checkmarks, highlights, and locks. I\'ve outlined activities for Spelling, Syllable division, Word sorting, and a Detective sentence checker, culminating in a customizable success page.\n\n\n"
    modified_response: "I will create the `/src/components/Mascot.tsx` component. This represents \"Lumi\", our educational dragon character. It uses interactive SVG vectors that dynamically adjust face expressions (eyes, mouth, colors) based on the child\'s performance (idle, correct, incorrect, cheering), giving immersive and welcoming encouragement in German."
    thinking_duration {
      seconds: 2
      nanos: 579381831
    }
    stop_reason: STOP_REASON_STOP_PATTERN
  }
