    modified_response: "I will create `/src/components/StationSyllables.tsx` for Station 2: Silben-H\303\274pfen. I will model the syllable cards as \"Boing-bouncing steps\" or \"lilypads\" floating on simulated creek waters. Children select the correct syllables in order (e.g. \"WAS\" then \"SER\") to help a frog mascot or Lumi cross the stream. I\'ll also add distractors (incorrect syllables) to provide a rewarding challenge and supportive guidance."
