    modified_response: "I will create `/src/App.tsx` to tie together the entire gamified German primary school experience. It contains the local state engine (persisted in `localStorage`), a lovely personalized welcome screen (where kids choose character avatars and custom nicknames), lessons, a progress header displaying collected stars, complete mascot interaction states, a station completion celebration modal, and navigation routes."
